name: Kedai Top
address: VJ3F+2JR, Jl. Singaraja-Gilimanuk, Pemuteran, Kec. Gerokgak, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81155, Indonesia
review 1:
This place looks small from the road but they have a large and beautiful seating area at the back with a stage for musical performances.
I ordered Ikan Baker (Grilled fish) and it was delicious.
And I got a free musical performance show from the owner and his family.
